      "text": "המלך: (דף לב:) <i data-commentator=\"Mishneh Torah, Prayer and the Priestly Blessing\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Sefer Mitzvot Gadol\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Tur\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i>חסידים",
