      "text": "פניך: אפילו <i data-commentator=\"Mishneh Torah, Prayer and the Priestly Blessing\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Sefer Mitzvot Gadol\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Tur\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i>המלך שואל בשלומו",
      "segment_ids": [
